column2: SELECT m.object_id, m.ra, m.dec, n.objid, n.distance, f.z, f.zErr, sm.logMass, sm.logMass_err, sm.ssfr + sm.logMass - #. AS logSFR, sm.age into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.oii_eo AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS f ON n.objid = f.objid JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as sm on f.SpecObjID = sm.SpecObjID
